      "acceptanceCriteria": "Solver must demonstrate correct implementation of governing equations through benchmark test cases at MRL 2 level.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent has been verified against standard CFD benchmark cases including lid-driven cavity and backward-facing step. Code verification documentation provided by vendor and confirmed applicable to incompressible viscous flow regime relevant to blood pump simulation."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Discretization error",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
