      "rationale": "Validation performed on the FDA generic centrifugal pump, which shares key geometric similarity (radial impeller, volute housing) with the CPB device under assessment. Blood analog fluid (glycerin-water mixture) used in experiments. Validation domain sufficiently overlaps COU operating space to support MRL 2 credibility claim."
