    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required level for MRL 2. The 6 non-assessed factors are acceptable at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 4. CFD model is accepted as credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. The relative hemolysis index predictions are conservative and support the RH < 1 acceptance criterion with adequate confidence for the intended regulatory submission.",
